(/FlyBase/drosophila-anatomy-developmental-ontology/security)\n-   [Insights](/FlyBase/drosophila-anatomy-developmental-ontology/pulse)\n\n# allow 'multi-cell component structure' to contain complete cells #2008\n\nNew issue\n\nCopy link\n\nNew issue\n\nCopy link\n\nClosed\n\n[#2101](https://github.com/FlyBase/drosophila-anatomy-developmental-ontology/pull/2101)\n\nClosed\n\n[allow 'multi-cell component structure' to contain complete cells](#top)#2008\n\n[#2101](https://github.com/FlyBase/drosophila-anatomy-developmental-ontology/pull/2101)\n\nCopy link\n\nAssignees\n\n[![Clare72](https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/38460997?s=64&v=4)](/Clare72)\n\nLabels\n\n[VFBrelated to the nervous system/requested by VFB](https://github.com/FlyBase/drosophila-anatomy-developmental-ontology/issues?q=state%3Aopen%20label%3A%22VFB%22)related to the nervous system/requested by VFB[correctionincorrect information in the ontology needs fixing](https://github.com/FlyBase/drosophila-anatomy-developmental-ontology/issues?q=state%3Aopen%20label%3A%22correction%22)incorrect information in the ontology needs fixing[quickthis will not take long to implement](https://github.com/FlyBase/drosophila-anatomy-developmental-ontology/issues?q=state%3Aopen%20label%3A%22quick%22)this will not take long to implement\n\n[![@Clare72](https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/38460997?v=4&size=80)](https://github.com/Clare72)\n\n## Description\n\n[![@Clare72](https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/38460997?v=4&size=48)](https://github.com/Clare72)\n\n[Clare72](https://github.com/Clare72)\n\nopened [on Jan 31, 2025](https://github.com/FlyBase/drosophila-anatomy-developmental-ontology/issues/2008#issue-2823396040)\n\nIssue body actions\n\nI think this term was mainly intended to cover things like cell body rinds and neuropil regions (these are subclasses), but it is currently unsuitable for this as these structures may contain whole glia.\n\nCurrent def:  \n\"A structure consisting of multiple cell components but which is not itself a cell and does not have (complete) cells as a part.\"\n\nProposed def:  \n\"A structure mainly consisting of cell components, rather than complete cells.\"\n\nProposed comment:  \n\"May contain complete cells in addition to partial ones.\"\n\nIf broadening is problematic, we should make a superclass with the proposed definition and move CBRs and neuropils up.\n\n[@dosumis](https://github.com/dosumis)\n\nReactions are currently unavailable\n\n## Metadata\n\n## Metadata\n\n### Assignees\n\n-   [![@Clare72](https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/38460997?s=64&v=4)\n    \n    Clare72\n    \n    ](/Clare72)\n\n### Labels\n\n[VFBrelated to the nervous system/requested by VFB](https://github.com/FlyBase/drosophila-anatomy-developmental-ontology/issues?q=state%3Aopen%20label%3A%22VFB%22)related to the nervous system/requested by VFB[correctionincorrect information in the ontology needs fixing](https://github.com/FlyBase/drosophila-anatomy-developmental-ontology/issues?q=state%3Aopen%20label%3A%22correction%22)incorrect information in the ontology needs fixing[quickthis will not take long to implement](https://github.com/FlyBase/drosophila-anatomy-developmental-ontology/issues?q=state%3Aopen%20label%3A%22quick%22)this will not take long to implement\n\n### Type\n\nNo type\n\n### Projects\n\nNo projects\n\n### Milestone\n\nNo milestone\n\n### Relationships\n\nNone yet\n\n### Development\n\nNo branches or pull requests\n\n## Issue actions\n\n## Footer\n\n[](https://github.com)© 2026 GitHub, Inc.\n\n### Footer navigation\n\n-   [Terms](https://docs.github.com/site-policy/github-terms/github-terms-of-service)\n-   [Privacy](https://docs.github.com/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-privacy-statement)\n-   [Security](https://github.com/security)\n-   [Status](https://www.githubstatus.com/)\n-   [Community](https://github.community/)\n-   [Docs](https://docs.github.com/)\n-   [Contact](https://support.github.com?tags=dotcom-footer)\n-   Manage cookies\n-   Do not share my personal information\n\nYou can’t perform that action at this time.","metadata":{"truncated":false},"title":"https://github.com/FlyBase/drosophila-anatomy-developmental-ontology/issues/2008 (text/html; charset=utf-8)","time":{"start":1778904132071,"end":1778904132846}},"id":"prt_e2ef2e8de001x3ob6pMHpIarXo","sessionID":"ses_1d10d6d4effeezfdc41LhV3iY2","messageID":"msg_e2ef2d9d7001uF2elnCfHH5WWP"}}
