{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778904403410,"sessionID":"ses_1d10d6d4effeezfdc41LhV3iY2","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"functions.bash:33","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"git commit -m \"Revised UBERON:0005162 definition to allow whole cells in multi cell part structures\n\nCloses #3490\n\nUpdated 'multi cell part structure' (UBERON:0005162) textual definition from:\n  'A structure consisting of multiple cell components but which is not itself a cell and does not have (complete) cells as a part.'\nto:\n  'A structure mainly consisting of cell components, rather than complete cells.'\n\nAdded comment noting that such structures may contain complete cells in\naddition to partial ones. This aligns with the recent FBbt revision of\nFBbt:00007060 and resolves a long-standing inconsistency where many current\nsubclasses (e.g., nervous system regions containing glia) were implicitly\nexcluded by the old, overly restrictive definition.\n\n- Added xref to FBbt:00007060\n- Added term tracker link to issue #3490\n- Added dc-contributor for Clare Pilgrim (ORCID:0000-0002-1373-1705)\n- Added dcterms-date and created_by metadata\n\nSigned-off-by: @dragon-ai-agent\"","description":"Commit changes to uberon-edit.obo"},"output":"[scribe-v1-ai4curation-uberon-agent-config-v3-.-togetherai-moonshotai-Kimi-K2.6-iter1-issue-3490 4967bb3] Revised UBERON:0005162 definition to allow whole cells in multi cell part structures\n 1 file changed, 7 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)\n","metadata":{"output":"[scribe-v1-ai4curation-uberon-agent-config-v3-.-togetherai-moonshotai-Kimi-K2.6-iter1-issue-3490 4967bb3] Revised UBERON:0005162 definition to allow whole cells in multi cell part structures\n 1 file changed, 7 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)\n","exit":0,"description":"Commit changes to uberon-edit.obo","truncated":false},"title":"Commit changes to uberon-edit.obo","time":{"start":1778904403406,"end":1778904403409}},"id":"prt_e2ef6f7a80016JEkZK1weGq6Q2","sessionID":"s